      "rolls": "",
      "goto": "",
      "link": "12",
      "is_end": false,
      "node_type": "normal",
      "children": {
        "9": {
          "id": "9",
          "speaker": "Jaheira",
          "text": "You think me lonely? In truth, I prefer travel in a small pack such as this.",
          "context": "NodeContext: Arched eyebrow, vaguely amused at why we're checking on her",
          "checkflags": [],
          "setflags": [],
          "ruletags": [],
          "approval": [],
          "rolls": "",
          "goto": "",
          "link": "12",
          "is_end": false,
          "node_type": "normal",
          "children": {
            "15": {
              "id": "15",
              "speaker": "Jaheira",
              "text": "Unburdened by numbers, we're free to act - rather than react. A little like the old days.",
              "context": "",
              "checkflags": [],
              "setflags": [],
              "ruletags": [],
              "approval": [],
              "rolls": "",
              "goto": "",
              "link": "12",
              "is_end": false,
              "node_type": "normal",
              "children": {
                "19": {
                  "id": "19",
                  "speaker": "Jaheira",
                  "text": "With allies every bit as peculiar - give or take a few tadpoles.",
                  "context": "NodeContext: Vaguely amused",
                  "checkflags": [],
                  "setflags": [],
                  "ruletags": [],
                  "approval": [],
                  "rolls": "",
                  "goto": "",
                  "link": "12",
                  "is_end": false,
                  "node_type": "normal",
                  "children": {
                    "2": {
                      "id": "2",
                      "speaker": "Player",
                      "text": "I'd like to hear more about those old days.",
                      "context": "",
                      "checkflags": [],
                      "setflags": [],
                      "ruletags": [],
                      "approval": [],
                      "rolls": "",
                      "goto": "",
                      "link": "12",
                      "is_end": false,
                      "node_type": "normal",
                      "children": {
                        "21": {
                          "id": "21",
                          "speaker": "Jaheira",
                          "text": "Would you? In time, then. Perhaps once you've found a rocking chair for me to doze off in.",
                          "context": "NodeContext: Amused that we're asking about stories of the good old days, but more focused on the task at hand. Putting us off, but not harshly.",
                          "checkflags": [],
                          "setflags": [],
                          "ruletags": [],
                          "approval": [],
                          "rolls": "",
                          "goto": "",
                          "link": "12",
                          "is_end": false,
                          "node_type": "normal",
                          "children": {}
                        }
                      }
                    },
                    "20": {
                      "id": "20",
                      "speaker": "Player",
                      "text": "Your experience will be an asset.",
                      "context": "",
                      "checkflags": [],
                      "setflags": [],
                      "ruletags": [],
                      "approval": [],
                      "rolls": "",
                      "goto": "",
                      "link": "12",
                      "is_end": false,
                      "node_type": "normal",
                      "children": {
                        "3": {
                          "id": "3",
                          "speaker": "Jaheira",
                          "text": "Hah! A kind way of saying: 'Ye gods, I hope her dusty bones don't break at the first blow.'",
                          "context": "NodeContext: Snort of amusement",
                          "checkflags": [],
                          "setflags": [],
                          "ruletags": [],
                          "approval": [
                            "Jaheira 2"
                          ],
                          "rolls": "",
                          "goto": "",
                          "link": "12",
                          "is_end": false,
                          "node_type": "normal",
                          "children": {
                            "23": {
                              "id": "23",
                              "speaker": "Jaheira",
                              "text": "Fear not for me. I will try my very best to keep up.",
                              "context": "NodeContext: Dryly amused. Your abilities are being questioned due to your age - you look forward to surprising the questioner.",
                              "checkflags": [],
                              "setflags": [],
                              "ruletags": [],
                              "approval": [],
                              "rolls": "",
                              "goto": "",
                              "link": "12",
                              "is_end": false,
                              "node_type": "normal",
                              "children": {}
                            }
                          }
                        }
                      }
                    },
                    "10": {
                      "id": "10",
                      "speaker": "Player",
                      "text": "Just try to keep up, old one.",
                      "context": "",
                      "checkflags": [],
                      "setflags": [],
                      "ruletags": [],
                      "approval": [],
                      "rolls": "",
                      "goto": "",
                      "link": "12",
                      "is_end": false,
                      "node_type": "normal",
                      "children": {
                        "4": {
                          "id": "4",
                          "speaker": "Jaheira",
                          "text": "Do you know, maybe my hearing is not what it was. Would you like to repeat that?",
                          "context": "NodeContext: Playing into the joke of her being old - but a friendly note of threat at the end",
                          "checkflags": [],
                          "setflags": [],
                          "ruletags": [],
                          "approval": [
                            "Jaheira 2"
                          ],
                          "rolls": "",
                          "goto": "",
                          "link": "12",
                          "is_end": false,
                          "node_type": "normal",
                          "children": {}
                        }
                      }
                    },
                    "22": {
                      "id": "22",
                      "speaker": "Player",
                      "text": "I wanted to ask about something else.",
                      "context": "",
                      "checkflags": [],
                      "setflags": [],
                      "ruletags": [],
                      "approval": [],
                      "rolls": "",
                      "goto": "",
                      "link": "12",
                      "is_end": false,
                      "node_type": "normal",
                      "children": {
                        "6": {
                          "id": "6",
                          "speaker": "Jaheira",
                          "text": "Then ask.",
                          "context": "",
                          "checkflags": [],
                          "setflags": [],
                          "ruletags": [],
                          "approval": [],
                          "rolls": "",
                          "goto": "",
                          "link": "12",
                          "is_end": false,
                          "node_type": "normal",
                          "children": {}
                        }
                      }
                    }
                  }
                }
              }
            }
          }
        }
