      "children": {
        "26": {
          "id": "26",
          "speaker": "Jaheira",
          "text": "I have given you much reason to think that Harpers hoard secrets like precious stones. But I promise you, this was not some intrigue.",
          "context": "",
          "checkflags": [],
          "setflags": [
            "Jaheira_InParty_AskedWhySheKeptFamilySecret"
          ],
          "ruletags": [],
          "approval": [],
          "rolls": "",
          "goto": "",
          "link": "14",
          "is_end": false,
          "node_type": "normal",
          "children": {
            "32": {
              "id": "32",
              "speaker": "Jaheira",
              "text": "Just... plain and simple foolishness. As if by keeping clear of my family, I might keep them clear of the cult in turn.",
              "context": "",
              "checkflags": [],
              "setflags": [],
              "ruletags": [],
              "approval": [],
              "rolls": "",
              "goto": "",
              "link": "14",
              "is_end": false,
              "node_type": "normal",
              "children": {
                "18": {
                  "id": "18",
                  "speaker": "Jaheira",
                  "text": "And if this fight were to go against us, well... they had already done their mourning. Why visit it on them twice?",
                  "context": "",
                  "checkflags": [],
                  "setflags": [],
                  "ruletags": [],
                  "approval": [],
                  "rolls": "",
                  "goto": "",
                  "link": "14",
                  "is_end": false,
                  "node_type": "normal",
                  "children": {
                    "13": {
                      "id": "13",
                      "speaker": "Player",
                      "text": "You're right. That is extremely foolish.",
                      "context": "",
                      "checkflags": [],
                      "setflags": [],
                      "ruletags": [],
                      "approval": [],
                      "rolls": "",
                      "goto": "",
                      "link": "14",
                      "is_end": false,
                      "node_type": "normal",
                      "children": {
                        "31": {
                          "id": "31",
                          "speaker": "Jaheira",
                          "text": "Careful, now. Only I get to say it. And my daughter, apparently.",
                          "context": "",
                          "checkflags": [],
                          "setflags": [],
                          "ruletags": [],
                          "approval": [
                            "Jaheira 3"
                          ],
                          "rolls": "",
                          "goto": "",
                          "link": "14",
                          "is_end": false,
                          "node_type": "normal",
                          "children": {}
                        }
                      }
                    },
                    "17": {
                      "id": "17",
                      "speaker": "Player",
                      "text": "I understand. I think I would have done the same.",
                      "context": "",
                      "checkflags": [],
                      "setflags": [],
                      "ruletags": [],
                      "approval": [],
                      "rolls": "",
                      "goto": "",
                      "link": "14",
                      "is_end": false,
                      "node_type": "normal",
                      "children": {
                        "16": {
                          "id": "16",
                          "speaker": "Jaheira",
                          "text": "Well, if fool I be, then at least I'm in good company.",
                          "context": "",
                          "checkflags": [],
                          "setflags": [],
                          "ruletags": [],
                          "approval": [
                            "Jaheira 3"
                          ],
                          "rolls": "",
                          "goto": "",
                          "link": "14",
                          "is_end": false,
                          "node_type": "normal",
                          "children": {}
                        }
                      }
                    },
                    "7": {
                      "id": "7",
                      "speaker": "Player",
                      "text": "Admit it - you were just afraid of Rion.",
                      "context": "",
                      "checkflags": [],
                      "setflags": [],
                      "ruletags": [],
                      "approval": [],
                      "rolls": "",
                      "goto": "",
                      "link": "14",
                      "is_end": false,
                      "node_type": "normal",
                      "children": {
                        "8": {
                          "id": "8",
                          "speaker": "Jaheira",
                          "text": "Of course I was! You met her, did you not? The girl had opinions before she had teeth.",
                          "context": "",
                          "checkflags": [],
                          "setflags": [],
                          "ruletags": [],
                          "approval": [
                            "Jaheira 3"
                          ],
                          "rolls": "",
                          "goto": "",
                          "link": "14",
                          "is_end": false,
                          "node_type": "normal",
                          "children": {}
                        }
                      }
                    },
                    "28": {
                      "id": "28",
                      "speaker": "Player",
                      "text": "Do you have so little faith in our chances of victory?",
                      "context": "",
                      "checkflags": [],
                      "setflags": [],
                      "ruletags": [],
                      "approval": [],
                      "rolls": "",
                      "goto": "",
                      "link": "",
                      "is_end": false,
                      "node_type": "normal",
                      "children": {
                        "5": {
                          "id": "5",
                          "speaker": "Jaheira",
                          "text": "No. Quite the opposite, in fact. I hoped to greet my family when all the fighting was done.",
                          "context": "",
                          "checkflags": [],
                          "setflags": [],
                          "ruletags": [],
                          "approval": [],
                          "rolls": "",
                          "goto": "",
                          "link": "",
                          "is_end": false,
                          "node_type": "normal",
                          "children": {
                            "14": {
                              "id": "14",
                              "speaker": "Jaheira",
                              "text": "I was wrong to think I could keep my children from this fight. They're Baldurian born and bred - the only damned reason I root myself in this place.",
                              "context": "",
                              "checkflags": [],
                              "setflags": [],
                              "ruletags": [],
                              "approval": [],
                              "rolls": "",
                              "goto": "",
                              "link": "",
                              "is_end": false,
                              "node_type": "normal",
                              "children": {
                                "30": {
                                  "id": "30",
                                  "speaker": "Jaheira",
                                  "text": "This city is a cesspit. An open sewer of the soul, that taints us with its filth, and churns us out when all that is good has been stripped away.",
                                  "context": "",
                                  "checkflags": [],
                                  "setflags": [],
                                  "ruletags": [],
                                  "approval": [],
                                  "rolls": "",
                                  "goto": "",
                                  "link": "",
                                  "is_end": false,
                                  "node_type": "normal",
                                  "children": {
                                    "27": {
                                      "id": "27",
                                      "speaker": "Jaheira",
                                      "text": "It also happens to be their home - and so it is mine. Ugh... that might be the first time I have said that out loud.",
                                      "context": "",
                                      "checkflags": [],
                                      "setflags": [],
                                      "ruletags": [],
                                      "approval": [],
                                      "rolls": "",
                                      "goto": "",
                                      "link": "",
                                      "is_end": false,
                                      "node_type": "normal",
                                      "children": {
                                        "0": {
                                          "id": "0",
                                          "speaker": "Jaheira",
                                          "text": "Now come - we had best get to saving it, lest Rion turn her ire on us both.",
                                          "context": "",
                                          "checkflags": [],
                                          "setflags": [],
                                          "ruletags": [],
                                          "approval": [],
                                          "rolls": "",
                                          "goto": "",
                                          "link": "",
                                          "is_end": false,
                                          "node_type": "normal",
                                          "children": {
                                            "12": {
                                              "id": "12",
                                              "speaker": "",
                                              "text": "",
                                              "context": "",
                                              "checkflags": [],
                                              "setflags": [],
                                              "ruletags": [],
                                              "approval": [],
                                              "rolls": "",
                                              "goto": "",
                                              "link": "",
                                              "is_end": true,
                                              "node_type": "taganswer",
                                              "children": {}
                                            }
                                          }
                                        }
                                      }
                                    }
                                  }
                                }
                              }
                            }
                          }
                        }
                      }
                    }
                  }
                }
              }
            }
          }
        }
